---
// Extracted and Fixed Section

import background_heating_03Img from '../assets/images/background_heating_03.jpg';
import background_heating_03Img_1 from '../assets/images/background_heating_03.jpg';
import background_heating_03Img_2 from '../assets/images/background_heating_03.jpg';
---
<section id="bt_bb_section69e3d26038e32" class="bt_bb_section bt_bb_color_scheme_1 bt_bb_layout_boxed_1200 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_top_spacing_extralarge bt_bb_bottom_spacing_extralarge custom-parallax-section" style="; --section-primary-color:#ffffff; --section-secondary-color:#252525; position: relative;" data-bt-override-class="null">
  <div class="bt_bb_background_image_holder_wrapper">
    <div style="background-image: url('${background_heating_03Img.src}') !important; background-attachment: fixed !important; background-size: cover !important; background-position: center !important;" class="bt_bb_background_image_holder"></div>
    <div class="bg-overlay" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(14, 45, 78, 0.85) !important; z-index: 0;"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="bt_bb_port" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
    <div class="bt_bb_cell">
      <div class="bt_bb_cell_inner">
        <style is:global>
          .custom-parallax-section {
            padding-top: 100px !important;
            padding-bottom: 150px !important; /* Exactly mirrors Section 6's -150px margin so the edge lines up perfectly */
            background: none !important;
            color: #ffffff !important;
          }
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_headline_content {
            color: #ffffff !important;
          }
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_headline_content span {
            color: #ffffff !important;
          }
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_headline_content b {
            color: #51acfb !important; /* Force the bold accent words to be light blue like the original */
          }
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_text p {
            color: #ffffff !important;
          }
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_counter_holder, 
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_counter_text, 
          .custom-parallax-section .bt_bb_counter span {
            color: #ffffff !important;
          }

          /* Hide invisible theme separators that ruin perfect mathematical measurements */
          #bt_bb_section69e3d26038e32 .bt_bb_separator {
            display: none !important;
          }

          /* Mathematically center the Grid exactly between the Headline and the overlapping boxes */
          #bt_bb_section69e3d26038e32 > .bt_bb_port > .bt_bb_cell > .bt_bb_cell_inner > .bt_bb_row:nth-child(2) {
            margin-top: 80px !important;      /* Exact space above grid (from the title) */
            margin-bottom: 80px !important;   /* Exact space below grid (to the photo boxes) */
          }
        </style>
        <div class="bt_bb_row" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_row_holder"><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_center bt_bb_padding_normal bt_bb_animation_fade_in animate" style="; --column-width:12;" data-width="12" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><header class="bt_bb_headline bt_bb_style_square bt_bb_dash_none bt_bb_size_extralarge bt_bb_align_center" data-bt-override-class="null"><h2><span class="bt_bb_headline_content"><span>Deixar de fazer <b>Manutenção</b> para poupar <b>Dinheiro</b><br>
É como parar o <b>Relógio</b> para poupar <b>Tempo</b><br>
</span></span></h2></header><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_row bt_bb_column_gap_60" style="; --column-gap:60px;" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_row_holder"><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-4 col-xl-4 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_padding_normal" style="; --column-width:4;" data-width="4" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><div class="bt_bb_counter_holder bt_bb_size_xlarge" data-bt-override-class="null"><span class="bt_bb_counter animate" data-digit-length="2"><span class="onedigit p2 d6" data-digit="6"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span><span class="onedigit p1 d0" data-digit="0"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span></span><span class="bt_bb_counter_text">%</span></div><div class="bt_bb_text"><p>Sabia que 60% do uso doméstico de água, é feito principalmente pelas casas de banho, jardim e cozinha?</p></div><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-4 col-xl-4 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_padding_normal" style="; --column-width:4;" data-width="4" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><div class="bt_bb_counter_holder bt_bb_size_xlarge" data-bt-override-class="null"><span class="bt_bb_counter animate" data-digit-length="3"><span class="onedigit p3 d6" data-digit="6"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span><span class="onedigit p2 d8" data-digit="8"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span><span class="onedigit p1 d1" data-digit="1"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span></span><span class="bt_bb_counter_text">L</span></div><div class="bt_bb_text"><p>A família média pode desperdiçar 681 litros de água anuais com vazamentos e falhas na canalização.</p></div><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div></div><div class="bt_bb_column col-xxl-4 col-xl-4 bt_bb_vertical_align_top bt_bb_align_left bt_bb_padding_normal" style="; --column-width:4;" data-width="4" data-bt-override-class="{}"><div class="bt_bb_column_content"><div class="bt_bb_column_content_inner"><div class="bt_bb_counter_holder bt_bb_size_xlarge" data-bt-override-class="null"><span class="bt_bb_counter animate" data-digit-length="3"><span class="onedigit p3 d1" data-digit="1"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span><span class="onedigit p2 d2" data-digit="2"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span><span class="onedigit p1 d0" data-digit="0"><span class="n0">0</span><span class="n1">1</span><span class="n2">2</span><span class="n3">3</span><span class="n4">4</span><span class="n5">5</span><span class="n6">6</span><span class="n7">7</span><span class="n8">8</span><span class="n9">9</span><span class="n0">0</span></span></span><span class="bt_bb_counter_text">€</span></div><div class="bt_bb_text"><p>Pode poupar mais de 120€ todos os anos se fizer manutenção regular e reparações imediatas em caso de falhas nas suas instalações.</p></div><div class="bt_bb_separator bt_bb_border_style_none bt_bb_bottom_spacing_medium" data-bt-override-class="null"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section>